FBIS3-52542 "drnes004_a_94004" FBIS-NES-94-004 Document Type:Daily Report 6 Jan 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Citizens Without Legal Status To Be Drafted LD0501205794 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1200 GMT 5 Jan 94 LD0501205794 Algiers ENTV Television Network Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] A statement by the National Defense Ministry informs citizens who do not have legal status that, with respect to the national military service -- exemption, deferment, renewal, postponment, or disability -- from 15 January they will be drafted immediately upon their apprehension in accordance with the laws in force.
